title: Watch Dubai’s craziest jaw-dropping stunt: 5 men fly through world's tallest hotel at 200km/h
summary_full: Five elite wingsuit athletes from XDubai executed a daring precision flight around the world's tallest hotel, Ciel Dubai Marina, reaching speeds over 200 km/h. The stunt, including a pass through the "eye of the needle," celebrated the hotel's grand opening and highlighted Dubai's strategy of fusing tourism, bold design and sky-high experiences.
